reconsider n = ( - k ) as (Element of ( NAT )) by A5,INT_1:3;
( k + l ) = ( m - n );
hence ( a #Z ( k + l ) ) = ( ( a |^ m ) / ( a |^ n ) ) by A1,CKB54:1
.= ( ( a |^ m ) * ( ( a |^ n ) " ) )
.= ( ( a |^ ( abs l ) ) * ( ( a |^ n ) " ) ) by ABSVALUE:def 1
.= ( ( a |^ ( abs l ) ) * ( ( a |^ ( abs ( - k ) ) ) " ) ) by ABSVALUE:def 1
.= ( ( a |^ ( abs l ) ) * ( ( a |^ ( abs k ) ) " ) ) by COMPLEX1:52
